#30503
Temple of Sonari~
This is the temple of the goddess of truth and light, Sonari.
You feel peaceful as you enter this huge cathedral. The walls are
golden and engraved with beautiful scenes of heroes of past ages.
The air is filled with the sounds of a choir of angels hovering in
the air above the altar. The altar itself is huge, made of gold and
glows with a holy aura. To the side of the altar is a statue of a
young, handsome priest. Standing by the statue smiling is the most 
beautiful woman you have ever seen. She glows with a holy light all
her own. She looks happily at the statue. This must be Sonari,
studying her statue of Randell to pass the time until his return.
The priests in the room, dressed all in white, stand ready to attend
to your needs. Peace, serenity and joy overcome you as you realize
this is the final resting place for the souls who follow the paths
of light.
~
