The Grand Banquet Hall~
This luxurious room is filled with dozens of green glass chairs lined up
along long tables made of blue glass. Elaborate stained glass mosaics of
crabs, seahorses and octopi line the walls just above eye level, and the
overall effect is quite striking. A very soft rug in shades of white and
violet reaches almost to the walls. To your east, you can see a swinging
door.
~
