#30574
An Abandoned Kitchen~
You are in a kitchen, immaculately clean, but completely empty. No cooking
implements are to be seen anywhere. It seems the further you explore this
place, the stranger it gets. How would anyone who was staying here eat?
If no one is here, why is it all so clean? A tiny shiver runs up your spine
as you try to decide what to do next. The equally empty banquet room lies
back to the west.
~
