A Narrow Trail~
You follow a narrow trail that winds among the dense, colorful foliage that
grows from the rich sand. You are surprised to find such lush plant life on
an island this rocky, but nonetheless, leaves rustle all around you, giving
the place a feeling of life. To the east, the plants thin out to the beach,
and to the west they become slightly thicker yet.
