On the Lush Lawn~
In sharp contrast to the multicolored, rocky earth of the rest of this
island, you now find yourself standing on a thick carpet of green, healthy
grass. A birdbath stands nearby, overflowing with water, and across this
green expanse to the west, the Glass Hotel looms up from the earth.
~
